high_descs: Walk forward and face the tub on your left.
Take out the dirty towel on the right.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left.
Put the dirty towel in the sink, wash it, and take it out.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the clean towel on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Take a dirty towel from the tub to clean it.

high_descs: Move towards bathroom counter.  Turn right and face the tub.
Grab the wash rag on the right.
Turn all the way around.  Go towards the wall.  Turn right and face the sink.
Put the wash rag in the sink.  Turn the water on.  Turn the water off.  Pick up the wash rag.
Turn all the way around and go towards the toilet.
Put the wash rag to the right of the blue bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Get the wash rag, get it wet to place it on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Pick up the rag on the right from the tub.
Bring the rag to the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink with water.
Pick up the rag from the sink and bring it to the toilet.
Put the rag on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Clean the rag on the right, put it on the toilet lid.
